# BuildKit reads this (named <dockerfile>.dockerignore) because the build
# context is the PARENT dir. Patterns are relative to that context root, which
# holds acdp-playground/ and acdp-rs/ side by side. Keep the context small and
# never ship local venvs, caches, the Rust target dir, or gitignored plans.
**/.git
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/node_modules
**/.DS_Store
acdp-playground/plans
acdp-playground/.claude
acdp-playground/.env
acdp-rs/target
